                li(style='--i: 8')
                    h3 Professional ethics and social values
                    p Ability to carry out any task with professional ethics and with out deviating from social values.
                li(style='--i: 9')
                    h3 Self-awareness and emotional intelligence
                    p An ability to recognize their own Strength and weekness and balance their own emotions at the time of crisis.
                li(style='--i: 10')
                    h3 Entrepreneurship qualities
                    p An ability to acquire entrepreneurship qualities and to take efforts to became entrepreneurs.
                li(style='--i: 11')
                    h3 Responsibility towards society and environment
                    p Realizing the responsibilities towards the society and to protect the environment, use ours professional knowledge for providing better living condition to the people. 
                li(style='--i: 12')
                    h3 Thirst for knowledge through lifelong learning
                    p Recognize the need for, and have the preparation and ability to engage in independent and life-long learning in the broadest context of technological change. 

